  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Judge:</strong> +2 to hit when both pistols are fired at the same target for an entire round. <br /><br /><strong>Jury:</strong> When firing both pistols at a target, gain +4 saves against any spells or abilities of that target until the start of your next turn.<br /><br /><strong>Continuance:</strong> When either of the pistols kills a target to CON or performs a Coup De Grace to kill a target, both are fully repaired, reloaded with 12 of the last bullet fired, and any jams are cleared.<br /><br /></p><img src=\"Art%20-%20Items/weapons/guns/folken88_magical_unholy_pair_of_pistols_dark_gothic_modern_sett_8bbe9f76-9980-4a19-b339-f772d66dd690.webp\" />",
